import React from 'react'
import { Container, Input, InputConatiner, LogoImg, Menu, Row, Wrapper } from './styles'

const Header = () => {

        <Container>
            <Row>
                <LogoImg src='./logo.webp' alt='logo'/>
                <InputConatiner>
                    <Input placeholder="buscar..."/>
                </InputConatiner>
                <Menu>live code</Menu>
                <Menu>Global</Menu>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </Wrapper>
  )
}

export {Header}
